Package: hangman
Title: Play a game of hangman in the console
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Alexander",
             family = "Rossell Hayes",
             role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
             email = "alexander@rossellhayes.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9412-0457")),
      person(given = "Centre for Translation Studies, University of Leeds",
             role = "cph"),
      person(given = "Luis",
             family = "Von Ahn",
             role = "cph"))
Description: Creates an interactive game in the console. Try to reveal a
  randomly selected word by guessing letters. If you make six incorrect
  guesses, you lose. Includes a list of 10,000 common English words with more
  than three letters.
